t California pizza bar</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Shane-Hawkins-Dave-Grohl-Chad-Smith@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Shane Hawkins performs at the Taylor Hawkins Tribute in 2022, Dave Grohl of Foo Fighters perform onstage during Harley-Davidson&#039;s Homecoming Festival in 2023 and Chad Smith of Red Hot Chili Peppers performs during Lollapalooza at Grant Park on August 06, 2023" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Shane-Hawkins-Dave-Grohl-Chad-Smith@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Shane-Hawkins-Dave-Grohl-Chad-Smith@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Shane-Hawkins-Dave-Grohl-Chad-Smith@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Shane-Hawkins-Dave-Grohl-Chad-Smith@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Shane-Hawkins-Dave-Grohl-Chad-Smith@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Shane-Hawkins-Dave-Grohl-Chad-Smith@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">Dave Grohl</a> , Chad Smith and Shane Hawkins have come together to play a series of rock classics at a pizza bar in California. Check out fan-captured footage of the moment below.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-wembley-foo-fighters-cover-3306358">Inside the Taylor Hawkins Tribute Concert: “A gigantic fucking night for a gigantic fucking person”</a></strong></li></ul><p> The intimate, star-studded set took place at the Rock N Roll Pizza Bar in Simi Valley, California on Monday evening (August 21), and was part of a set by famous covers band Chevy Metal.</p><p> The band was formed by late drummer <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-hawkins">Taylor Hawkins</a> , who often performed with the side project in his time away from his <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a> commitments. Now, over a year since his death in Colombia, the band&#39;s frontman took to the stage to play with the band, as did his teenage son, Shane.</p><p> Kicking off the set with Grohl on the guitar and backing vocals, the band opened their 17-song set with a cover of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-police">The Police</a> – playing their 1978 track &#39;Next To You&#39;. From there, they immediately launched into more rock classics, including &#39;Jailbreak&#39; by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thin-lizzy">Thin Lizzy</a> and &#39;Bitch&#39; by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">The Rolling Stones</a> .</p><p> Three back-to-back covers of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/van-halen">Van Halen</a> tracks were included – &#39;Everybody Wants Some!!&#39;, &#39;Jamie&#39;s Cryin&#39; and &#39;Unchained&#39; – as were renditions of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/led-zeppelin">Led Zeppelin</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">Black Sabbath</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/motley-crue">Mötley Crüe</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kinks">The Kinks</a> . </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Chevy Metal w/ Dave Grohl - Stage Entrance &amp; &quot;Next to You&quot;, Rock &amp; Roll Pizza, Simi Valley, 8.21.23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6vLuTcird-M?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Chevy Metal w/ Dave Grohl &quot;Bitch&quot;, Rock &amp; Roll Pizza, Simi Valley, CA, 8.21.23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HQaP8qlyNgU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Chevy Metal &quot;Moby Dick&quot; w/ Shane Hawkins&#039; drum solo, Rock &amp; Roll Pizza, Simi Valley, CA, 8.21.23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sUyOeQEwXEc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> It was mid-way through the set, however, when lucky onlookers got another surprise from the star-studded band, as during their performance of a fourth Van Halen song the band were joined by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janes-addiciton">Jane&#39;s Addiction</a> &#39;s Stephen Perkins.</p><p> He joined them for the latter half of &#39;Ain&#39;t Talkin&#39; &#39;bout Love&#39;, as well as performances of &#39;Tie Your Mother Down&#39; by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queen">Queen</a> and &#39;Moonage Daydream&#39; by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a> .</p><p> During the encore, another surprise drummer took to the kit – Chad Smith of <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a> . He joined Grohl and co. for the final track of the evening, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/acdc">AC/DC&#39;</a> s 1976 hit track &#39;Dirty Deeds Done Dirt Cheap&#39;. Find more footage of the show below. </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Chevy Metal w/ Dave Grohl &amp; Stephen Perkins &quot;Ain&#039;t Talkin&#039; &#039;bout Love&quot;, Simi Valley, CA, 8.21.23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mDdpts_s6Lo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Chevy Metal w/ Dave Grohl &amp; Stephen Perkins &quot;Tie Your Mother Down&quot;,, Simi Valley, CA, 8.21.23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/FE7ua958dcM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Chevy Metal w/ Dave Grohl &amp; Chad Smith &quot;Dirty Deeds&quot;, Rock &amp; Roll Pizza, Simi Valley, CA, 8.21.23" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tK-Jdk0qOB0?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> This isn&#39;t the first time that Shane – the teenage son of the late Taylor Hawkins – has joined Chevy Metal on stage to show off his drumming skills. Earlier this month, the musician made headlines when <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-hawkins-son-shane-performs-led-zeppelin-black-sabbath-with-chevy-metal-3478262">he joined the band for a couple of shows in California, and performed Led Zeppelin and Black Sabbath tracks</a> alongside Skid Row frontman <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sebastian-bach">Sebastian Bach</a> .</p><p> He also made an <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/taylor-hawkins-tribute-concert-wembley-foo-fighters-cover-3306358">appearance at the mammoth tribute concerts, held for his father six months after his death</a> .</p><p> Taking to the stage to play a cover of Foo Fighters&#39; &#39;My Hero&#39; last September at Wembley Stadium, Shane&#39;s drumming was considered one of the standout moments of the concert, and led to him winning <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-hawkins-son-shane-wins-award-for-drum-performance-at-tribute-concert-3392157">a prestigious award for Drum Performance of the Year from the Drumeo Awards</a> .</p><p> As well as his emotional performance at the Taylor H